data.description: *Multiple Offers* Highest & Best due by 2/24/2021 at 5pm* This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on a quiet street is full of updates and is move-in ready! Brand NEW AC being installed 3/1/2021!! Upon entering you will immediately notice the new waterproof laminate flooring throughout. The kitchen is nice and open with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and views of the spacious backyard. The master bedroom and ensuite bathroom are on the back of the house offering lots of privacy while the two additional bedroom are spacious and share a newly updated guest bathroom. You will fall in love with the fully fenced huge backyard with a spacious concrete patio, pergola with covered seating area, fire pit, and plenty of room for a boat, playground, pool, and more! No HOA or deed restrictions here! Additional features of this home are inside laundry room, crown molding, spacious front patio sitting area, new interior paint, and updated ceiling fans throughout. This home is perfect for a commuter with its easy access to I75/275 or even a second home with a short drive to the award winner Anna Maria Island beaches! This home is a must see! Schedule your showing today.
